cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.Medical Imaging, cs.DL 

The paper deals with the segmentation of kidneys from CT data, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The usage of geodesic distance volumes as an additional source of information is a novel approach that involves mathematical concepts (cs.DL). Finally, the application of the proposed method is in the field of medical imaging (cs.Medical Imaging).
